Story_Texts.SourceString: Ugh I'm so bored with this place already. More ice?
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Ugh I'm so bored with this place already. More ice?

Story_Texts.SourceString: What's wrong, Drake? Do you wish there was a water level?
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: What's wrong, Drake? Do you wish there was a water level?

Story_Texts.SourceString: Even water would be better than this. Boring!
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Even water would be better than this. Boring!

Story_Texts.SourceString: The ice used to melt every spring.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: The ice used to melt every spring.

Story_Texts.SourceString: Now it is bound in a mighty, freezing stranglehold.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Now it is bound in a mighty, freezing stranglehold.

Story_Texts.SourceString: Maybe you can melt the ice with that dumb sword of yours, Drake!
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Maybe you can melt the ice with that dumb sword of yours, Drake!

Story_Texts.SourceString: Mew will find interesting things to fight!
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Mew will find interesting things to fight!
